    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a refreshed VANOS system. The suspension maintains its composure with upgraded bushings, ensuring the chassis stays planted during high-lateral-G maneuvers. A mechanically sound driver\u2019s car with an unmistakable induction note and sharp throttle response.",
