      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-cared-for model that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish that looks stunning in person, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is free of tears, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, benefiting from a recent comprehensive service and a fresh set of tires. It tracks straight, brakes firmly, and the engine delivers smooth, consistent power through all gears. This is a non-smoker's car that has been primarily garage-kept, and it comes complete with a documented service history and all original manuals. It is ready to provide its next owner with many miles of dependable and stylish transportation.",
